程序包 sokobanfx.model

类 Level

java.lang.Object
sokobanfx.model.Level
所有已实现的接口:
java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>
public final class Level
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>
Level class is used for generates two game grids and detect the game status of current level.

    LevelIterator provides the interface to iterate through the GameGrid containing the GameObjects for the current Level.
